---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="SP-194 Artifact｜Human Feedback Packet"
  description="一個無 API 的互動 demo：把 Agent 的 Markdown 文字牆變成可操作的 HTML review surface，再匯出成下一輪 prompt。"
>
  <section class="artifact-page" aria-labelledby="artifact-title">
    <div class="ambient ambient-one"></div>
    <div class="ambient ambient-two"></div>

    <header class="hero-card">
      <p class="eyebrow">SP-194 companion artifact</p>
      <h1 id="artifact-title">HTML 不是比較漂亮的輸出，是人類回到 Agent 迴圈的控制面板</h1>
      <p class="hero-copy">
        這頁不呼叫任何 AI API。你只是在瀏覽器裡 review 一份 Agent 產出的「分享按鈕」規格，
        做幾個人類判斷，然後匯出一包可以貼回 Claude Code / Codex / OpenClaw 的 feedback packet。
      </p>
      <div class="hero-actions" aria-label="Page actions">
        <a class="warm-button" href="#review-surface">開始互動</a>
        <a class="ghost-button" href="/posts/sp-194-20260508-trq212-html-markdown-agent/"
          >回到 SP-194</a
        >
      </div>
    </header>

    <section class="loop-strip" aria-label="Agentic loop overview">
      <article>
        <span>01</span>
        <strong>Agent output</strong>
        <p>先丟出一坨看起來很完整、但很難 review 的 Markdown。</p>
      </article>
      <article>
        <span>02</span>
        <strong>Human surface</strong>
        <p>人類不用逐字改，改用 chips、choices、priority 做判斷。</p>
      </article>
      <article>
        <span>03</span>
        <strong>Feedback packet</strong>
        <p>頁面把判斷整理成下一輪 prompt。沒有 API，也能完整閉環。</p>
      </article>
    </section>

    <section class="demo-grid" id="review-surface">
      <article class="markdown-wall" aria-labelledby="wall-title">
        <div class="panel-heading">
          <p class="eyebrow">Before</p>
          <h2 id="wall-title">Agent 的 Markdown 文字牆</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="wall-paper">
          <p><strong>Feature:</strong> Add share button to gu-log article pages</p>
          <p>
            We should add a share button near the article title and maybe at the bottom. It should
            support copying the URL, maybe native share on mobile, and maybe X / Telegram. It should
            look nice and not distract users. Need to think about whether tracking is okay, whether
            mobile browsers support Web Share API, whether fallback copy works, and whether the
            button should be visible before or after reading.
          </p>
          <p>
            Risks: modal might be annoying, external share links might leak referrer, icons might
            add bundle size, native share might fail silently, and analytics could make the feature
            feel creepy. Also if the button looks too loud it might cheapen the reading experience.
          </p>
          <p>
            Next steps: implement component, add tests, check mobile, add copy state, maybe add
            tooltip, update docs, decide whether share button belongs in header, footer, or both.
          </p>
        </div>
        <p class="wall-caption">
          內容不一定錯。問題是人類很容易看完第一段就開始滑手機。這就是 SP-194 說的：瓶頸不是 AI
          會不會寫，是人類願不願意 review。
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="surface-card" aria-labelledby="surface-title">
        <div class="panel-heading">
          <p class="eyebrow">After</p>
          <h2 id="surface-title">Human review surface</h2>
        </div>

        <div class="control-group">
          <h3>這顆分享按鈕第一版應該服務誰？</h3>
          <div class="segmented" data-control="audience" role="group" aria-label="Audience">
            <button
              type="button"
              class="active"
              data-value="mobile readers who just finished an article">手機讀者</button
            >
            <button
              type="button"
              data-value="friends who might enjoy gu-log but need one clean link">朋友</button
            >
            <button
              type="button"
              data-value="future ShroomDog reviewing what made the article digestible"
              >未來的 ShroomDog</button
            >
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="control-group">
          <h3>第一版 priority</h3>
          <div class="priority-list" aria-label="Priority list">
            <button
              type="button"
              class="priority-chip active"
              data-priority="Native share on mobile first">1. 手機 native share</button
            >
            <button
              type="button"
              class="priority-chip active"
              data-priority="Copy link fallback with clear success state"
              >2. Copy link fallback</button
            >
            <button
              type="button"
              class="priority-chip"
              data-priority="Social network buttons only if they do not add visual noise"
              >3. 社群按鈕先不要吵</button
            >
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="control-group">
          <h3>請 Agent 優先修的風險</h3>
          <div class="chip-cloud" data-control="risks" aria-label="Risk choices">
            <button
              type="button"
              class="active"
              data-value="Do not add tracking or dark-pattern sharing pressure">不要追蹤壓迫</button
            >
            <button
              type="button"
              class="active"
              data-value="Mobile copy/share fallback must be obvious">手機 fallback 清楚</button
            >
            <button type="button" data-value="Keep the visual weight quieter than the article title"
              >視覺重量別搶戲</button
            >
            <button type="button" data-value="Avoid a modal unless it clearly reduces friction"
              >避免 modal</button
            >
            <button
              type="button"
              data-value="External share targets must not become the whole feature"
              >別變社群貼紙牆</button
            >
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="control-group slider-group">
          <label for="warmth">文案溫度：<span id="warmth-label">友善但不油</span></label>
          <input id="warmth" type="range" min="0" max="3" value="2" />
        </div>
      </article>
    </section>

    <section class="packet-card" aria-labelledby="packet-title">
      <div class="panel-heading">
        <p class="eyebrow">Export</p>
        <h2 id="packet-title">Feedback Packet</h2>
      </div>
      <p>
        這段就是要貼回 Agent 的東西。HTML 沒有幫你「呼叫 AI」，但它幫你把人類判斷整理成 Agent
        能繼續工作的 context。
      </p>
      <textarea id="feedback-packet" readonly aria-label="Generated feedback packet"></textarea>
      <div class="packet-actions">
        <button type="button" class="warm-button" id="copy-packet">Copy feedback packet</button>
        <span id="copy-status" role="status" aria-live="polite"></span>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="easter-card" aria-labelledby="easter-title">
      <div>
        <p class="eyebrow">Tiny easter egg</p>
        <h2 id="easter-title">你剛 review 了一個 Agent。也順手 review 一下 gu-log？</h2>
        <p>
          如果你覺得 gu-log 有趣，分享給一個朋友。<br />
          如果你覺得 gu-log 很無聊，也請分享給 ShroomDog：ShroomDog 對「怎麼把無聊內容變好入口」非常有興趣。
        </p>
      </div>
      <button type="button" class="ghost-button" id="copy-easter">Copy gu-log share note</button>
    </section>

    <section class="example-section" aria-labelledby="examples-title">
      <p class="eyebrow">Same loop, other surfaces</p>
      <h2 id="examples-title">分享按鈕只是第一個例子</h2>
      <div class="example-grid">
        <article>
          <span>Notification Settings</span>
          <h3>把「不要吵我」變成可選策略</h3>
          <p>讓人類選哪些通知該預設安靜、哪些真的值得打斷，再匯出成 UX spec。</p>
        </article>
        <article>
          <span>Onboarding Flow</span>
          <h3>把新手流程從 checklist 變成排序板</h3>
          <p>拖出 friction、must-have、can-skip，讓 Agent 重寫更不煩人的 first-run experience。</p>
        </article>
        <article>
          <span>Search / Filter UI</span>
          <h3>把 filter 邏輯變成可 review 的決策</h3>
          <p>針對 mobile、empty state、排序規則做選擇，再把 decisions 貼回 Agent。</p>
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style is:inline>
  @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Fraunces:opsz,wght@9..144,600;9..144,750&family=Noto+Sans+TC:wght@400;500;700;800&display=swap');

  .artifact-page {
    --cream: #fff4dc;
    --cream-2: #f7e5c1;
    --ink: #3c2417;
    --muted: #7c5d49;
    --orange: #e76f32;
    --orange-dark: #b94d22;
    --honey: #f6b44b;
    --leaf: #6b8f6b;
    --card: rgba(255, 250, 238, 0.88);
    --line: rgba(106, 71, 42, 0.18);
    width: min(1120px, calc(100vw - 1.5rem));
    margin: 1.25rem 0 0 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    position: relative;
    color: var(--ink);
    font-family: 'Noto Sans TC', sans-serif;
  }

  :global([data-theme='dark']) .artifact-page,
  :global([data-theme='light']) .artifact-page {
    color: var(--ink);
  }

  .artifact-page::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: -1rem -0.75rem;
    border-radius: 36px;
    background:
      radial-gradient(circle at 18% 8%, rgba(246, 180, 75, 0.45), transparent 30%),
      radial-gradient(circle at 85% 2%, rgba(231, 111, 50, 0.22), transparent 28%),
      linear-gradient(135deg, #fff7e8 0%, var(--cream) 42%, #f4ddb5 100%);
    z-index: -2;
    box-shadow: 0 24px 80px rgba(48, 27, 9, 0.22);
  }

  .ambient {
    position: absolute;
    border-radius: 999px;
    filter: blur(8px);
    opacity: 0.5;
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: -1;
  }

  .ambient-one {
    width: 170px;
    height: 170px;
    right: 3%;
    top: 90px;
    background: rgba(246, 180, 75, 0.42);
  }

  .ambient-two {
    width: 120px;
    height: 120px;
    left: 4%;
    top: 470px;
    background: rgba(107, 143, 107, 0.24);
  }

  .hero-card,
  .loop-strip article,
  .markdown-wall,
  .surface-card,
  .packet-card,
  .easter-card,
  .example-grid article {
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    background: var(--card);
    box-shadow: 0 18px 40px rgba(83, 49, 20, 0.12);
    backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
  }

  .hero-card {
    padding: clamp(1.35rem, 4vw, 3rem);
    border-radius: 34px;
    overflow: hidden;
    position: relative;
  }

  .hero-card::after {
    content: '🐾';
    position: absolute;
    right: clamp(1rem, 5vw, 3rem);
    bottom: -0.35rem;
    font-size: clamp(3.2rem, 13vw, 8rem);
    opacity: 0.13;
    transform: rotate(-10deg);
  }

  .eyebrow {
    margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
    color: var(--orange-dark);
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: 0.13em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .hero-card h1,
  .packet-card h2,
  .easter-card h2,
  .example-section h2,
  .panel-heading h2 {
    font-family: 'Fraunces', 'Noto Sans TC', serif;
    color: var(--ink);
    letter-spacing: -0.04em;
  }

  .hero-card h1 {
    max-width: 820px;
    margin: 0;
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 7vw, 4.65rem);
    line-height: 0.96;
  }

  .hero-copy {
    max-width: 760px;
    margin: 1.25rem 0 0;
    color: var(--muted);
    font-size: clamp(1rem, 2.2vw, 1.18rem);
    line-height: 1.9;
  }

  .hero-actions,
  .packet-actions {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    margin-top: 1.25rem;
  }

  .warm-button,
  .ghost-button {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    min-height: 46px;
    padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
    border-radius: 999px;
    font: inherit;
    font-weight: 800;
    text-decoration: none;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition:
      transform 0.18s ease,
      box-shadow 0.18s ease,
      background 0.18s ease;
  }

  .warm-button {
    border: 0;
    color: #fff9ed;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--orange), var(--honey));
    box-shadow: 0 12px 24px rgba(196, 83, 33, 0.24);
  }

  .ghost-button {
    border: 1px solid rgba(185, 77, 34, 0.35);
    color: var(--orange-dark);
    background: rgba(255, 249, 237, 0.7);
  }

  .warm-button:hover,
  .ghost-button:hover {
    transform: translateY(-1px);
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .loop-strip {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 0.85rem;
    margin: 1rem 0;
  }

  .loop-strip article {
    border-radius: 24px;
    padding: 1rem;
  }

  .loop-strip span {
    display: inline-grid;
    place-items: center;
    width: 34px;
    height: 34px;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    border-radius: 12px;
    color: var(--orange-dark);
    background: rgba(231, 111, 50, 0.14);
    font-weight: 900;
  }

  .loop-strip strong {
    display: block;
    color: var(--ink);
  }

  .loop-strip p,
  .wall-caption,
  .packet-card p,
  .easter-card p,
  .example-grid p {
    color: var(--muted);
  }

  .demo-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 0.92fr) minmax(0, 1.08fr);
    gap: 1rem;
    align-items: stretch;
  }

  .markdown-wall,
  .surface-card,
  .packet-card,
  .easter-card,
  .example-section {
    border-radius: 30px;
    padding: clamp(1rem, 3vw, 1.5rem);
  }

  .panel-heading h2,
  .packet-card h2,
  .easter-card h2,
  .example-section h2 {
    margin: 0 0 0.8rem;
    font-size: clamp(1.45rem, 3vw, 2rem);
  }

  .wall-paper {
    padding: 1rem;
    border-radius: 18px;
    color: #6d625d;
    background:
      repeating-linear-gradient(0deg, rgba(88, 69, 52, 0.06) 0 1px, transparent 1px 28px),
      rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.62);
    font-size: 0.92rem;
    line-height: 1.62;
    box-shadow: inset 0 0 0 1px rgba(75, 48, 26, 0.08);
  }

  .control-group {
    padding: 1rem;
    border: 1px solid rgba(106, 71, 42, 0.13);
    border-radius: 22px;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45);
  }

  .control-group + .control-group {
    margin-top: 0.75rem;
  }

  .control-group h3,
  .slider-group label {
    display: block;
    margin: 0 0 0.65rem;
    color: var(--ink);
    font-size: 1rem;
  }

  .segmented,
  .chip-cloud,
  .priority-list {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }

  .segmented button,
  .chip-cloud button,
  .priority-chip {
    border: 1px solid rgba(124, 93, 73, 0.22);
    border-radius: 999px;
    background: #fff9ed;
    color: var(--muted);
    font: inherit;
    font-weight: 700;
    padding: 0.62rem 0.78rem;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.16s ease;
  }

  .segmented button.active,
  .chip-cloud button.active,
  .priority-chip.active {
    border-color: rgba(231, 111, 50, 0.45);
    color: var(--orange-dark);
    background: rgba(231, 111, 50, 0.14);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 18px rgba(231, 111, 50, 0.12);
  }

  .slider-group input {
    width: 100%;
    accent-color: var(--orange);
  }

  .packet-card,
  .easter-card,
  .example-section {
    margin-top: 1rem;
  }

  #feedback-packet {
    width: 100%;
    min-height: 260px;
    margin-top: 0.75rem;
    padding: 1rem;
    border: 1px solid rgba(106, 71, 42, 0.18);
    border-radius: 20px;
    color: #463126;
    background: #fffaf0;
    font:
      0.9rem/1.65 ui-monospace,
      SFMono-Regular,
      Menlo,
      Consolas,
      monospace;
    resize: vertical;
  }

  #copy-status {
    color: var(--leaf);
    font-weight: 800;
  }

  .easter-card {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr auto;
    gap: 1rem;
    align-items: center;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255, 250, 238, 0.94), rgba(255, 228, 179, 0.82));
  }

  .example-section {
    padding-inline: 0;
  }

  .example-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 0.85rem;
  }

  .example-grid article {
    border-radius: 24px;
    padding: 1rem;
  }

  .example-grid span {
    color: var(--orange-dark);
    font-size: 0.76rem;
    font-weight: 900;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .example-grid h3 {
    margin: 0.4rem 0;
    color: var(--ink);
    font-size: 1.05rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 840px) {
    .loop-strip,
    .demo-grid,
    .example-grid,
    .easter-card {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .artifact-page {
      width: min(100%, calc(100vw - 1rem));
    }
  }
</style>

<script is:inline>
  const state = {
    audience: 'mobile readers who just finished an article',
    risks: [
      'Do not add tracking or dark-pattern sharing pressure',
      'Mobile copy/share fallback must be obvious',
    ],
    priorities: ['Native share on mobile first', 'Copy link fallback with clear success state'],
    warmth: 2,
  };

  const warmthLabels = ['乾淨直接', '克制友善', '友善但不油', '有一點 Clawd 式調皮'];
  const packet = document.getElementById('feedback-packet');
  const warmth = document.getElementById('warmth');
  const warmthLabel = document.getElementById('warmth-label');
  const copyStatus = document.getElementById('copy-status');

  function renderPacket() {
    const text = `Human Feedback Packet: Share Button v1\n\nWhat I understood:\n- The feature is not "add more social icons."\n- The real goal is to help a reader share a gu-log article at the moment they find it useful, without making the reading experience feel cheap or pushy.\n\nDecisions I made:\n- Primary audience: ${state.audience}.\n- Tone: ${warmthLabels[state.warmth]}.\n- Priorities:\n${state.priorities.map((item, index) => `  ${index + 1}. ${item}`).join('\n')}\n\nRisks to fix first:\n${state.risks.map((item) => `- ${item}`).join('\n')}\n\nNext prompt for the agent:\nPlease revise the share button plan around these human decisions. Keep the first version small: mobile native share, copy-link fallback, no tracking pressure, and visual weight quieter than the article itself. Return a concise implementation plan plus edge cases for mobile browsers.`;

    if (packet instanceof HTMLTextAreaElement) packet.value = text;
  }

  function setActiveButton(button, group) {
    group.querySelectorAll('button').forEach((item) => item.classList.remove('active'));
    button.classList.add('active');
  }

  document.querySelectorAll('[data-control="audience"]').forEach((group) => {
    group.addEventListener('click', (event) => {
      const button = event.target instanceof HTMLButtonElement ? event.target : null;
      if (!button) return;
      state.audience = button.dataset.value || state.audience;
      setActiveButton(button, group);
      renderPacket();
    });
  });

  document.querySelectorAll('[data-control="risks"] button').forEach((button) => {
    button.addEventListener('click', () => {
      const value = button.dataset.value || '';
      button.classList.toggle('active');
      if (button.classList.contains('active')) {
        if (!state.risks.includes(value)) state.risks.push(value);
      } else {
        state.risks = state.risks.filter((item) => item !== value);
      }
      renderPacket();
    });
  });

  document.querySelectorAll('.priority-chip').forEach((button) => {
    button.addEventListener('click', () => {
      const value = button.dataset.priority || '';
      button.classList.toggle('active');
      if (button.classList.contains('active')) {
        if (!state.priorities.includes(value)) state.priorities.push(value);
      } else {
        state.priorities = state.priorities.filter((item) => item !== value);
      }
      renderPacket();
    });
  });

  warmth?.addEventListener('input', () => {
    if (!(warmth instanceof HTMLInputElement)) return;
    state.warmth = Number(warmth.value);
    if (warmthLabel) warmthLabel.textContent = warmthLabels[state.warmth];
    renderPacket();
  });

  async function copyText(text) {
    if (navigator.clipboard) {
      await navigator.clipboard.writeText(text);
      return;
    }
    const temp = document.createElement('textarea');
    temp.value = text;
    document.body.appendChild(temp);
    temp.select();
    document.execCommand('copy');
    temp.remove();
  }

  document.getElementById('copy-packet')?.addEventListener('click', async () => {
    const text = packet instanceof HTMLTextAreaElement ? packet.value : '';
    await copyText(text);
    if (copyStatus) copyStatus.textContent = 'Copied. 這包 feedback 可以貼回 Agent 了。';
  });

  document.getElementById('copy-easter')?.addEventListener('click', async () => {
    await copyText(
      '我剛讀到 gu-log 的 SP-194 companion artifact：它用一個分享按鈕 demo 解釋 HTML 怎麼讓人類回到 Agent loop。覺得有趣可以分享給朋友；覺得無聊也可以丟回 ShroomDog，因為 ShroomDog 正在研究怎麼把無聊內容變好入口。 https://gu-log.vercel.app/artifacts/sp-194-html-loop/'
    );
    if (copyStatus) copyStatus.textContent = 'Easter egg note copied. Share wisely. 🐾';
  });

  renderPacket();
</script>
